        "timestamp": "2019-06-13 11:33:07.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\nThanks Arind.\nPlease note this change is incorrect, as the exception is rethrown and logged on a different place.\nSonar is mistaken here, as he does not understand the convention of unwrapping UncheckedExecutionException and rethrowing as unchecked using ExceptionUtils.rethrow:\n\n```\n      catch (UncheckedExecutionException exception) {\n            return ExceptionUtils.rethrow(exception.getCause());\n      }\n```",
